Module edu.uoc.trip
Package edu.uoc.trip.model.cells

Class Cell

java.lang.Object
edu.uoc.trip.model.cells.Cell
Direct Known Subclasses:
MovableCell, RotatableCell
public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
Class that represents a static and non-rotatable cell of the board.
Both movable cells and rotatable cells inherit from this class, since these two classes are cells with special behaviour.
Author:
David García-Solórzano

      public boolean isMovable()
      Returns true if the cell is movable. Otherwise, it returns false.
